description:

[INCLUDED]

- Gosetsu Katsushika
- Tatsuki Bunkyo
- Masaru Kita
- Doshi Nakano

- Yui Itabashi

- Zakusa Ishigame

**This set is also contained in "Cardfight!! Vanguard Dear Days Digital Deluxe Edition".
**This set cannot be obtained duplicately. Please be aware of it if you are purchasing the Digital Deluxe Edition.
